      "writtenOn": "2020-04-02T00:07:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I forgot about this requirement. Since we now constructing a new copy of AuthMethod it is important. Handlers are installed in `standard.InstallHandlers(r)` which eventually calls https://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/refs/heads/master/appengine/gaeauth/server/default.go#41. I think we should allow server.CookieAuth to be assignable and replace it with tweaked \u0026openid.AuthMethod before standard.InstallHandlers(r). This will require changing some type assertions in https://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/refs/heads/master/appengine/gaeauth/server/default.go to account for arbitrary auth.Method. I think we\u0027ll also have to remove cookieAuthMethod wrapper (I\u0027m not quite sure why it exists, but it appears it discourages people from overriding server.CookieAuth). I can make this refactoring myself if you prefer.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 49,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 51,
        "endChar": 19
      },
      "revId": "d182834ffb7f237c24e9299ad7a4fee25725b286",
